### Admin Routes

#### [NEW] [routes/admin.js](file:///d:/nodejs/routes/admin.js)

| Route | Method | Chức năng |
|---|---|---|
| `/admin/upload` | GET | Trang upload video |
| `/admin/upload` | POST | Xử lý upload video |
| `/admin/videos` | GET | Danh sách video (sort theo thời gian) |
| `/admin/videos/:id/edit` | GET | Trang sửa video |
| `/admin/videos/:id/edit` | POST | Cập nhật video |
| `/admin/videos/:id/delete` | POST | Xoá video (DB + files) |
| `/admin/videos/:id/push-top` | POST | Đẩy video lên đầu |
| `/admin/servers` | GET | Danh sách server |
| `/admin/servers/add` | GET | Trang thêm server |
| `/admin/servers/add` | POST | Lưu server mới |
| `/admin/servers/:id/edit` | GET | Trang sửa server |
| `/admin/servers/:id/edit` | POST | Cập nhật server |
| `/admin/servers/:id/delete` | POST | Xoá server |

